cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper deals with the construction of deep learning models for image classification tasks on mobile and embedded devices. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel neural network architecture and discusses the training process, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the reduction of computational cost, which is related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
